{"tid":1512694,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"廢除香港關係法","createTime":"2019-08-28T03:50:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T08:30:00.000Z","uid":28534,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9c0a90722ba36f9abb89eb9badb525dec9f5c3e1","tid":1512694,"uid":28534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T03:50:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-abolish-united-states-hong-kong-policy-act-if-hong-kong-implement-emergency-regulations-ordinance\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequest-abolish-united-states-hong-kong-policy-act-if-hong-kong-implement-emergency-regulations-ordinance&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQw1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=4d63b730\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-abolish-united-states-hong-kong-policy-act-if-hong-kong-implement-emergency-regulations-ordinance</a><br />\n<br />\n林鄭咁想用緊急法，一於等大家一齊攬炒。<br />\n<br />\nHong Kong people is fighting against the the 'Extradition Bill' and the Government responds by police brutality and neglects what people are requesting. Now, there is rumour that the government will implement 'Emergency Regulations Ordinance' to suppress the rebellion of people against the brutality of the establishment.<br />\nThis Ordinance allows the government to 'suppress publications, writings, maps, plans, photographs, communications and means of communication' and empowers the government on 'appropriation, control, forfeiture and disposition of property' . This article empowers the government without limit of power and the Ordinance clearly defies human rights. Therefore, we request the US government to act accordingly and abolish the 'United States&ndash;Hong Kong policy act'."},{"pid":"ac75558811dc9dd3fd280986424fb474232ca328","tid":1512694,"uid":150331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T03:51:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf